README

 4DTRIS
 Created by Simon, Laszlo 

 This Application is a Tetris game extended to 4 dimensions. The 
 visualization uses OpenGL and GLUT. 

 ---

 Preinstall for bzr version:
 $ ./autogen.sh

 Install:
 $ ./configure
 $ make
 $ make install
 
 Run:
 $ 4dtris
  
